These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, november, october
3 different games are played: bridge, billiard, mah-jongg
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, lilac, ivory
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, montecristo, bolivar
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, musical, horror
 1. the person watching horror movies is the person playing billiard##1
 2. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing billiard is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person who likes chestnut is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is in the middle##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the swisher-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite        | lemonade |
| Birthday          | october    | november        | december    |
| Game   | mah-jongg        | bridge        | billiard    |
| Color           | ivory        | chestnut    | lilac   |
| Cigar         | montecristo    | bolivar | swisher |
| Movie-Genre     | musical     | scientific          | horror     |

