.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different games are played: chess, monopoly, snooker
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, paramedic, software-developer
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, january, march
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, pear, kiwi
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, mauve, lavender
City: hamburg, san-francisco, boston
1. the electrician is the person eating kiwi##1
2. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the electrician is on the left of the software-developer##1
4. the person who likes mauve is on the far left##1
5. the person playing chess is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
8. the electrician is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |         3          |
| Game         | snooker    | chess     | monopoly            |
| Job           | paramedic | electrician | software-developer |
| Birthday   | november    | january      | march             |
| Food   | eggplant | kiwi     | pear             |
| Color         | mauve  | lavender       | emerald           |
| City     | boston     | san-francisco   | hamburg            |

