.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, skydiving, video-games
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, country, dubstep
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, oliveros, old-henry
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, almond-milk
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, daffodil, tulip
There 3 different types of food: lime, strawberry, cauliflower
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the fan of disco##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is the bongani-smoker##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
6. the person who growstulip is the person eating lime##1
7. the person who growspoppy is the oliveros-smoker##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
9. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3       |
| Hobby         | video-games  | cooking     | skydiving    |
| Music-Genre           | country | disco  | dubstep |
| Cigar   | old-henry       | bongani | oliveros      |
| Beverage   | milk     | almond-milk      | lemonade     |
| Flower           | tulip          | daffodil      | poppy   |
| Food     | lime          | cauliflower       | strawberry    |

