3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, prince, siglo
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, may, june
House: ranch-style, cape-cod, wooden
 1. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
 2. the wooden house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 3. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 4. the ritmeester-smoker is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the wooden house##1
 6. the person who likes turquise is the siglo-smoker##1
 7. the wooden house is the person who likes amber##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 9. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who likes green##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |
| Flower          | poppy | iris | marigold        |
| Hobby         | fishing  | dancing   | reading     |
| Color           | turquise  | amber | green |
| Cigar   | siglo  | ritmeester   | prince     |
| Birthday   | may  | november  | june      |
| House           | cape-cod   | wooden       | ranch-style        |

