There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, 7up
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, poppy, zinnia
3 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, chess
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the journalist is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person playing canasta is the person who likes yellow##1
4. the person who likes red is on the right of the german##1
5. the person who growspoppy is the french##1
6. the lawyer is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the lawyer is on the far left##1
8. the person drinking sprite is the lawyer##1
9. the australian is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |
| Nationality          | german  | australian       | french    |
| Color         | yellow | red     | lavender      |
| Job           | lawyer  | journalist | scientist    |
| Beverage   | sprite   | milk  | 7up |
| Flower   | zinnia     | marigold       | poppy      |
