 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
 8. the person playing billiard is on the right of the architect##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3       |
