3 different games are played: snooker, billiard, monopoly
There are 3 different nationalities: french, german, australian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, skateboarding, tennis
 1. the person driving the bike is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
 3. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
 4. the german is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 5. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the old-henry-smoker is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 8. the person traveling to london is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
10. the person playing snooker is the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| City      | london    | paris     | berlin         |
| Cigar          | siglo  | ritmeester    | old-henry         |
| Transport           | helicopter | bike | jet-ski          |
| Game   | snooker    | monopoly      | billiard        |
| Nationality   | australian     | french     | german          |
| Sport         | tennis    | biathlon | skateboarding |

