.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-1-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, azure, emerald
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, scientist, lawyer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, game, siglo
City: berlin, boston, new-york
3 different pets are kept: bird, cat, mouse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, martial-arts, scientific
1. the game-smoker is in the middle##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is the person who likes azure##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is the accountant##1
6. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1
7. the lawyer is the owner of the cat##1
8. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
9. the scientist is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3       |
| Color          | azure          | emerald      | black      |
| Job         | lawyer        | scientist | accountant      |
| Cigar   | vegafina          | game        | siglo       |
| City   | berlin       | boston   | new-york      |
| Pet           | cat           | mouse      | bird         |
| Movie-Genre         | scientific | time-travel    | martial-arts |

 